Usage:

Scrapy: https://doc.scrapy.org/en/latest/intro/overview.html
pausing and resuming crawl: https://doc.scrapy.org/en/latest/topics/jobs.html


scrapy crawl WikiEvent -o [any location/][any file name, Ex:WikiEvent].jl

jl stand for JSON Lines format http://jsonlines.org/

for other format:
    json format use filename.json 
    csv  format use filename.csv -t csv